OL,7,FEvery household should have an
OL,8,Femergency pack that includes three
OL,9,Fdays worth of food and water according
OL,10,Fto the government, in new advice
OL,11,Fissued today.
OL,13,FThe Deputy Prime Minister, Oliver
OL,14,FDowden, launched a new website today
OL,15,Faimed at
OL,17,FThe advises people on how to protect
OL,18,Fthemselves from risks ranging from
OL,19,Ffloods and power outages to cyber
OL,20,Fattacks and .
