OL,3,CBatteries, wet wipes and wind-up
OL,4,Cradios: Government issues new
OL,5,Cemergency advice
OL,7,FIt urges households to put together an
OL,8,F"emergency kit" of items, including
OL,9,Fbottled water, spare batteries and a
OL,10,Fwind-up radio.
OL,12,FPortable power banks, battery torches,
OL,13,Ffirst aid kits and hand sanitiser are
OL,14,Falso recommended, as well as extra
OL,15,Fbaby supplies for those who need them.
OL,17,FIn a speech at the London defence
OL,18,Fconference, Mr Dowden said that he is
OL,19,Fnot being a "doomsday prepper", but
OL,20,Frather setting out "sensible
OL,21,Fsafeguards."
