OL,4,Cradios: Government issues new
OL,5,Cemergency advice
OL,7,FA poll by the conference showed that
OL,8,Fonly 15% of people have an emergency
OL,9,Fsupply kit in their homes, and more
OL,10,Fthan 40% do not have three days'
OL,11,Fsupply of non-perishable items.
OL,13,F"One thing that Covid made clear is
OL,14,Fthat crises can hit us all in ways we
OL,15,Fmight not be able to anticipate and
OL,16,Fthat ," he said.
OL,18,FBut he urged people against
OL,19,F"stockpiling".
