OL,7,FThe new website also offers advice on
OL,8,Fhow to get involved in community
OL,9,Factivities before, during, and after
OL,10,Femergencies; and also offers advice on
OL,11,Fcoping with trauma.
OL,13,FIt also offers specific advice for
OL,14,Fdisabled people and their carers.
OL,16,FLast year, the government introduced a
OL,17,Fnew, meaning all mobile phones get
OL,18,Fsent a loud alert sound if there is a
OL,19,Fnearby emergency.
